column2: Is your employer primarily a tech company/organization?
column3: Does your employer provide mental health benefits as part of healthcare coverage?
column4: Do you know the options for mental health care available under your employer-provided health coverage?
column5: Has your employer ever formally discussed mental health (for example, as part of a wellness campaign or other official communication)?
column6: Does your employer offer resources to learn more about mental health disorders and options for seeking help?
column7: Is your anonymity protected if you choose to take advantage of mental health or substance abuse treatment resources provided by your employer?
column8: If a mental health issue prompted you to request a medical leave from work, how easy or difficult would it be to ask for that leave?
column9: Would you feel comfortable discussing a mental health issue with your direct supervisor(s)?
column10: Have you ever discussed your mental health with your employer?
column11: Overall, how much importance does your employer place on physical health?
column12: Overall, how much importance does your employer place on mental health?
column13: Overall, how well do you think the tech industry supports employees with mental health issues?
